              </author>
              <colophon>Colophon: iti śrīsvamneśvarācāryaviracite śāṃḍilyaśatasūtrīyabhāṣye tṛtīyādhyāyasya dvitīyamānhikaṃ samāptaścāyamadhyāyaḥ samāptāceyaṃtrilakṣaṇā bhaktimīmāṃsā (f. 59r).</colophon>
